Note on third-party assets:

The `clawd` pixel-art assets (referenced under `themes/clawd-dev/` for local
development only) are NOT covered by this MIT license. Those assets originate
from the `clawd-on-desk` project (https://github.com/rullerzhou-afk/clawd-on-desk),
which is licensed under AGPL-3.0, and are intentionally excluded from this
repository's version control. End users / contributors who wish to use those
assets locally must fetch them separately and comply with the AGPL-3.0 terms.
The DeskPet repository itself ships no AGPL-licensed code or assets.
